{"tid":2406324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲休學！正妹YouTuber「20歲就買下百萬名車」　還有奢華獨棟豪宅","createTime":"2021-02-13T06:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T07:13:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":198,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"81309858d54484986562471f9083ff966f94794c","tid":2406324,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"YouTuber成為時下新興職業，因為入行門檻及年齡不受限制，許多年輕人趨之若鶩，若是一炮而紅就能一夕成名，同時也能賺進大把鈔票。馬來西亞當紅的YouTuber「Findy」年僅21歲，粉絲已經累積超過72萬人，日前買下人生的第2輛車，要價上百萬，讓許多網友自嘆不如。<br />\n<br />\nFindy外型可愛清純，除了經營YouTube頻道，在抖音上也有高人氣，4年已有超過72萬人追蹤，近日她在IG宣布買下人生的第2輛車，是要價200萬的賓士名車，開心寫道：「算是我送給我自己的21歲生日禮物，這是獎勵自己這幾年的努力，接下來也要更努力100倍！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5452/d5452731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5452%2Fd5452731.jpg&h=394a4bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5452/e5452733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5452%2Fe5452733.jpg&h=c2949754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Findy才20歲就買下豪宅和名車。（圖／翻攝自Findy IG）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Findy在2020年10月就買下人生第一間房，實現了一直以來的願望，她曾透露自己因為喜歡拍攝，當年果斷決定放棄學業，當起全職YouTuber，經過不斷努力，也終於有收穫，對於外界質疑她是靠父母買房買車，她則強調這全都是自己賺錢得來的，絕對沒有拿家裡一毛錢。<br />\n<br />\n20歲就入手百萬名車，其實Findy的第一台車是馬來西亞的國產車，價格相當親民，不少網友自嘆不如，「我20歲存款都還是零」、「我現在25歲，連車子都還買不起」、「恭喜恭喜，19歲的我很壓力」、「真的很勵志」、「願意付出努力就會有收穫」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5452/d5452732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5452%2Fd5452732.jpg&h=b7c54c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Findy才20歲就買下豪宅和名車。（圖／翻攝自Findy IG）"},{"pid":"6000f77b4df5c8797776d1736a5b0edfa2b339f4","tid":2406324,"uid":255310,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"一分鍾開兩個Po咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67d63279ddc0cc354d585a98e0a38a2be492ce7","tid":2406324,"uid":155818,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"邊能個?"},{"pid":"b7753be97f36a96fa8953f3e0b11e56aefb77423","tid":2406324,"uid":64337,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"都幾樣衰"},{"pid":"3d101ee80fe00418a1ebf62d66e67a45a907b8fb","tid":2406324,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"我老婆<br />\nThx"},{"pid":"998d18a7140025652b7b09d83dd1e78a5ba9ffa1","tid":2406324,"uid":3764,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7Y2uEn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7Y2uEn.png&h=ca879ea8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92b5642824e61ee37066995435fa59c7fef38af7","tid":2406324,"uid":251945,"like":69,"dislike":7,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"住父母屋企嘅連登仔又要屌人臭雞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af839ff6017c0266f0eeddbb9ef1410d804cf9b8","tid":2406324,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3986e348fbafc1fbef48862c17642a3f9d95a4","tid":2406324,"uid":73,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"二手cla都要晒?"},{"pid":"4babf1402084610f448577bc1d3a214a6b073fdd","tid":2406324,"uid":38904,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"998d18a7140025652b7b09d83dd1e78a5ba9ffa1","tid":2406324,"uid":3764,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7Y2uEn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7Y2uEn.png&h=ca879ea8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"大馬嘅八達通?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /